</emphasis>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFBD72E3FFF47B57FF0BF88435A40E52" author="Holloway JD" box="[205,394,1803,1827]" pageId="15" pageNumber="1116" pagination="1 - 529" refId="ref11463" refString="Holloway JD (2005) The moths of Borneo (parts 15 &amp; 16): family Noctuidae, subfamily Catocalinae. The Malayan Nature Journal 58: 1 - 529." type="journal article" year="2005">Holloway (2005)</bibRefCitation>
. This species can be easily distinguish by its yellow hind wings with two black bands and black tinged yellow abdomen. Forewing is having reniform black or obscure.
